These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, french, italian, british
1. the french is in an odd position##4
2. the british is between the argentine and the french##2
3. the british is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | argentine | british | french | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, cabbage, plum, cucumber
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating cabbage is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | cabbage | asparagus | cucumber | plum |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, family, action, disaster
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the person watching thriller movies##3
2. the person watching thriller movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching action movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching family movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | disaster | action | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: parkour, tennis, golf, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
2. the person who's sport is golf is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is golf##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | tennis | parkour | skateboarding | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, climbing, ice-hockey, surfing
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | surfing | badminton | ice-hockey | climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, indian, italian, russian
1. the indian is on the far right##1
2. the indian is on the left or right of the russian##3
3. the italian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | italian | dutch | russian | indian |

