1. the entrepreneur is on the left or right of the nurse##3
2. the nurse is in an odd position##4
3. the fisherman is between the entrepreneur and the freelancer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Job   | nurse | entrepreneur | fisherman | freelancer |

