2. the person watching crime movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | martial-arts | scientific | crime |

