2. the person eating watermelon is on the left or right of the person eating asparagus##3
3. the person eating asparagus is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating cucumber is in an even position##4
5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | asparagus | watermelon | onion | cucumber |

